_sText:
I'm using the P_Warehouse Prefab as a base for this AIM Map.
Layout: GrayTap
P_Warehouse Prefab: Razo18
http://www.fpsbanana.com/prefabs/590

Included is a NAV file and the bots do offer excellent game play, they have so far made use of every obstacle and vantage point except for the catwalk in the rafters, perhaps the ladders are to high!

If I remember correctly there are 32 spawn points per team!
no buy zone, players start with knife, pistol; on the ground are limited grenades and mp5 rifles.

please leave feed back...

this map is now running in a 3 map rotation on my server...
here is a link to my server...
http://sincitysource.graytap.com/
